Title: The Outing
Plot: No thanks to Elaine, Jerry must work hard to prove he is straight when a college reporter mistakenly reports that he and George are gay, "not that there is anything wrong with that." Things really get out of hand when the article is picked up by the New York Post.
GuestStars: Lawrence Mandley, Deck McKenzie, Liz Sheridan, Barney Martin, Estelle Harris, Paula Marshall, Kari Coleman, Anthony Mangano, Ben Reed, Charley Garrett, David Gibbs
